        "body": "\nThe balloon icon in the header (the green “dj” balloon) currently has no hover interaction.\nAdding a hover animation will improve the UI feel and make the header more interactive and lively — especially since the rest of the page has a celebration theme.\n\nCurrent Behavior ::\n\nThe balloon icon is static.\nHovering over it does not trigger any animation or visual feedback.\n\nExpected Behavior ::\n\n1. The balloon should slightly move, scale, bounce, or wobble.\n2. A small shadow or lift effect could be added for better depth.\n3. The animation should be subtle and smooth, not distracting.",
